en, G</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2012-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>56e2e5377c2ac3.03223656</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>3F8B953A-92CE-4184-BB5A-C331E2DCA40B</gtr:id><gtr:title>Global System Dynamics and Policies</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/5c5406ca581014deb6029efdcd5e89a3"><gtr:id>5c5406ca581014deb6029efdcd5e89a3</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Foden, G</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2010-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>56e2eada6082d8.63301877</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication><gtr:publication><gtr:id>3BBB0CBC-27C5-4980-BD9E-F5CC9B781FD1</gtr:id><gtr:title>Global System Dynamics and Policy: Best Practice Guidelines Towards a Science of Global Systems</gtr:title><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.ukri.org:80/person/999a12cb887a5ea3ba5e203fbcc2f88a"><gtr:id>999a12cb887a5ea3ba5e203fbcc2f88a</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Bishop, S</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2013-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:outcomeId>56e2e3855d8741.56366730</gtr:outcomeId></gtr:publication></gtr:publications><gtr:identifiers><gtr:identifier type="RCUK">AH/D502314/1</gtr:identifier></gtr:identifiers><gtr:healthCategories/><gtr:researchActivities/><gtr:researchSubjects><gtr:researchSubject><gtr:id>062860E1-C81F-4028-9095-19A5E6455C70</gtr:id><gtr:percentage>0</gtr:percentage><gtr:text>Languages &amp; Literature</gtr:text></gtr:researchSubject></gtr:researchSubjects><gtr:researchTopics><gtr:researchTopic><gtr:id>DE53E60A-FE46-433C-BA16-151F707B335F</gtr:id><gtr:percentage>0</gtr:percentage><gtr:text>Creative Writing</gtr:text></gtr:researchTopic><gtr:researchTopic><gtr:id>EF860896-6A4B-4EF6-A42E-F78E49ED901F</gtr:id><gtr:percentage>0</gtr:percentage><gtr:text>Post-Colonial Studies</gtr:text></gtr:researchTopic></gtr:researchTopics><gtr:rcukProgrammes/></gtr:project></gtr:projectComposition></gtr:projectOverview>